  <h1>Last year alone, Basecamp helped over 285,000 companies finish more than 2,000,000 projects.</h1>
</section>

<div class="home-signup">
  <a class="button button-active home-signup-mobile" href="/start">Give Basecamp a try</a>
  <a class="button button-active home-signup-desktop" href="/start">Give Basecamp a try - it&rsquo;s free for 60 days</a>
