<section>
  <h2>Highly recommended.</h2>
  <p>Primarily through word-of-mouth alone, Basecamp has become the world&rsquo;s #1 project management tool. For the last 10 years, companies have been switching to Basecamp because it&rsquo;s famously easy-to-use, reliable, and It Just Works&trade;. Combine that with our best-in-the-biz customer service, and you&rsquo;ve got a unique and delightful package. Just last week, another <span data-signups></span> companies <a href="/start">started using Basecamp</a>.</p>

  <h2>A track record you can trust.</h2>
  <p>We&rsquo;ve been in business for 15 years, so you can depend on us to be here when you need us. We&rsquo;re profitable, debt-free, and privately owned so we answer to our customers and no one else. Our job is to help you do your job better. <a href="/about">Learn more about our company</a>.</p>

  <h2>On the Mac, PC, iPhone/iPad, Android and via email.</h2>
  <p>Basecamp&rsquo;s at home on Safari (Mac, iPhone/iPad), Chrome (Mac, PC, iPhone/iPad, Android), Firefox (Mac, PC), and IE 9+ (PC, Surface). Basecamp also integrates effortlessly with email. Official apps are available for the <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/basecamp-official-app/id599139477?mt=8">iPhone in the App Store</a> and <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.basecamp.app">Android on Google Play</a>.</p>
</section>

